  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - III. Calendae maji.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Majus adest; da serta, puer; sic sancta vetustas</l>
     <l n="2">Instituit, prisci sic docuere patres.</l>
     <l n="3">Junge hederam violis, myrtum subtexe ligustris;</l>
     <l n="4">Alba verecundis lilia pinge rosis.</l>
     <l n="5">Fundat inexhaustos mihi decolor Indus odores:</l>
     <l n="6">Et fluat Assyrio sparsa liquore coma.</l>
     <l n="7">Grandia fumoso spument crystalla Lyaeo:</l>
     <l n="8">Et bibat, in calices lapsa corona meos.</l>
     <l n="9">Post obitum non ulla mihi carchesia ponet</l>
     <l n="10">Aeacus. Infernis non viret uva jugis.</l>
     <l n="11">Heu vanum mortale genus, quid gaudia differs?</l>
     <l n="12">Falle diem: mediis mors venit atra jocis.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
